thread.title: U.S. Team Leads World Championships
thread.title_full: U.S. Team Leads World Championships - The New York Times

author: The Associated Press
title: U.S. Team Leads World Championships
text:
The United States women’s gymnastics team dazzled during qualifying at the 2015 world championships Saturday in Glasgow, posting the top overall score to cement its status as heavy favorites for a repeat.
The group, led by the two-time defending all-around champion Simone Biles and the reigning Olympic champion Gabrielle Douglas, finished with a total 236.611, well ahead of second-place Russia, to secure a spot in Tuesday’s team final.
